Package org.eclipse.gef.ui.palette.customize

Interface Summary
EntryPage An EntryPage displays properties of a PaletteEntry.
EntryPageContainer An EntryPageContainer allows an EntryPage to report errors to it.
 

Class Summary
DefaultEntryPage This is a default implementation of the EntryPage interface.
DrawerEntryPage The default entry page for drawers.
PaletteContainerFactory Abstract factory for PaletteContainers This class does not create PaletteContainers within other PaletteContainers.
PaletteCustomizationAction PaletteCustomizationActions are used to manipulate the palette model.
PaletteCustomizerDialog This class implements a default dialog that allows customization of the different entries/items on a GEF palette, i.e. the model behind the palette.
PaletteDrawerFactory Factory to create categories
PaletteEntryFactory A PaletteEntryFactory creates certain type of PaletteEntries.
PaletteGroupFactory Factory to create groups
PaletteSeparatorFactory Factory to create PaletteSeparators.
PaletteSettingsDialog  
PaletteStackFactory Factory to create PaletteStack
